Package: bedscout
Title: Simple arithmetic and visualizations on BED files
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Carmen", "Navarro", , "carmen.navarro@scilifelab.se", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5438-9654"))
Description: bedscout is a small toolset to calculate intersection statistics
  among BED files and/or GRanges objects and visualize them in a comprehensive
  way.
